transforms.result: .page{margin:0 auto;max-width:1300px;position:relative}.navigation-tools{box-sizing:border-box;height:-moz-fit-content;height:fit-content;max-height:calc(100% - 110px);overflow:auto;padding:8px 0;position:fixed;transition:all .2s linear;width:-moz-fit-content;width:fit-content}.navigation-tools dd{letter-spacing:.5px;margin:0;padding:6px 0}.navigation-tools dd a{color:#5e5d5b;display:inline-block;font-size:14px;padding:2px 4px;text-decoration:none;transition:.1s}.navigation-tools dd a:hover{background:#ff5a00;border-radius:3px}.navigation-tools .nav_active a{background:transparent!important;color:#ff5a00}.tools-box{margin:0 auto;min-height:800px;width:1080px}.tools-box section{align-content:flex-start;background-color:#fff;border-radius:8px;display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:20px;min-height:166px;padding:42px 48px 10px;position:relative;width:100%}.tools-box section .point{left:0;opacity:0;position:absolute;top:-60px}.tools-box section header{border-bottom:.5px solid rgba(0,0,0,.07);flex-shrink:0;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;left:0;line-height:42px;padding-left:46px;position:absolute;top:0;width:100%}.tools-box section .tool-item{cursor:pointer;flex-shrink:0;height:42px;line-height:42px;width:164px}.tools-box section .tool-item img{height:20px;margin-right:5px;vertical-align:middle;width:20px}.tools-box section .tool-item .tool-name{color:rgba(0,0,0,.851);font-size:14px;vertical-align:middle}@media (max-width:480px){.navigation-tools{display:none}.tools-box{width:unset}.tools-box section{padding:58px 16px 16px}.tools-box section header{padding:0 16px}.tools-box section .tool-item{width:140px}}
